data.description: Welcome to 2422 Apricot Lane located just steps away from the Augusta National Golf Course! This all brick ranch style home offers delightful features including original hardwood floors.  Featuring three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home offers comfortable living for family of all sizes. Eat in kitchen and a large great room with built in bookshelves. A fully finished basement provides endless possibilities for additional living space, a home office, a home gym, or even a private theater - the choice is yours. Sit outside on your back patio & enjoy your private backyard that is fully fenced. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your new home in Augusta! Roof is less than 2 years old! NEW Windows! All appliances remain to include washer/dryer & refrigerator.
